Regarding implementation of Sindhuratna Samriddhi Yojana, No. In accordance with the provision under paragraph (5) of the Government Decision 1, the "Sindhuratna Executive Committee" shall consist of two special members in addition to the above-mentioned members.
The invited members will be appointed by the Planning Department. "Instead of this text" "Sindhuratna"
